                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18310407-98-off546 t18310407-98-crimeloc548"></join>, and saw the prisoner and another person standing against Mr. Welsford's shop - it struck me they were at no good; I passed them, then turned back, and crossed the road - I saw the other one go into the shop, and bring out something, which he gave the prisoenr; I caught the prisoner, and took him back with the two cloaks, which he was rolling up - he had a kind of fisherman's jacket on; the other ran away.</p>
